<h1>Books</h1>

<p>I love to read — mostly fiction, historical fiction, memoir, and the occasional sci-fi. Pulled automatically from <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/show/68621097-abby-krishnan">my Goodreads</a>.</p>

{% if goodreads.currentlyReading.length > 0 %}
<h2>Currently Reading</h2>
<ul class="book-list">
{% for book in goodreads.currentlyReading %}
  <li class="book-item">
    <span class="book-title">{{ book.title }}</span>
    <span class="book-author">by {{ book.author }}</span>
  </li>
{% endfor %}
</ul>
{% endif %}

<h2>Recently Read</h2>
<ul class="book-list">
{% for book in goodreads.read %}
  <li class="book-item">
    <span class="book-title">{{ book.title }}</span>
    <span class="book-author">by {{ book.author }}</span>
    {% if book.rating > 0 %}
    <span class="book-rating">
      {% for i in range(0, book.rating) %}★{% endfor %}{% for i in range(book.rating, 5) %}☆{% endfor %}
    </span>
    {% endif %}
  </li>
{% endfor %}
</ul>

<p class="divider">&#128218;</p>

<p class="more-books">...and {{ goodreads.totalRead - 10 }}+ more on <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/show/68621097-abby-krishnan">Goodreads</a>.</p>
